OL,5, The Treasury is considering removing a 
OL,6, cap on bankers' bonuses as part of a   
OL,7, post-Brexit shake-up of City rules.    
OL,9,FSources said no final decisions had    
OL,10,Fbeen made, but confirmed chancellor    
OL,11,FKwasi Kwarteng considered it a way of  
OL,12,Fmaking London a more attractive place  
OL,13,Ffor global banks to do business.       
OL,15,FCity bosses have long complained about 
OL,16,Fthe EU-wide bonus rules which cap      
OL,17,Fbonuses at twice an employee's salary. 
OL,19,FThey say they lead to higher base pay  
OL,20,Fthat pushes up banks' fixed costs.     
